    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Chronic tension-type headache

          -  Normal urine pH

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  More than 1 migraine attack/month

          -  Other major illnesses

          -  Overuse of medicine/alcohol

          -  Women not using AC

          -  Pregnant/breast-feeding women

          -  Allergy to memantine
      </textblock>
